# UI Standards

- Use tokenized Tailwind classes (bg-primary, text-foreground, border-border, bg-background).
- Prefer composing from `src/components/ui/*` primitives.
- Never use raw hex colors in components; use CSS vars or tokens only.
- Layout rhythm: `max-w-6xl/7xl`, `px-6`, `py-6`, `gap-6`.
- Typography: page titles `text-2xl/3xl`, section titles `text-lg`, body `text-sm/base`.
- Surfaces: use Card-like containers with `rounded-xl`, subtle borders, `shadow-sm`.
- Empty states include: icon, headline, helper text, primary CTA.
- Buttons: default primary orange; links should not be browser-default blue/underlined.
